{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_vrtx_01TJZL8yeCani8fqGM54MHRv","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Experiments 1-5 all have scripts and results. Experiment 6 (\"Enhancement Options (Integration)\") does not have a script yet. I need to create `output/06-enhancement-options.sh`.\n\nLet me understand what experiment 6 needs:\n- Test with supported configuration: `enableLazyInitialization=true`, `enableDirtyTracking=true`\n- Verify unsupported options (`enableAssociationManagement`, `enableExtendedEnhancement`) are not enabled or produce expected behavior when set\n\nI need to look at the existing scripts to understand the patterns used, especially the happy path and the integration tests.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1256,"cache_read_input_tokens":61800,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":1256,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":9},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"aa443835-14f9-43a2-a882-6515be006913","uuid":"9a8b2c42-c14e-401b-8052-c152c8a6fe3c","request_id":"req_vrtx_011CcCUmNg6x7urE5sQgJqXt"}
