{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_vrtx_01YGsNqf9y5B1yx6ffCJRddy","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the pattern. I need to create experiment 6: Enhancement Options (Integration). Let me also look at the existing results to understand the Hibernate version being used and the enhancement context better.\n\nFrom the experiment description:\n- Test with supported configuration: `enableLazyInitialization=true`, `enableDirtyTracking=true`\n- Verify unsupported options (`enableAssociationManagement`, `enableExtendedEnhancement`) are not enabled or produce expected behavior when set\n\nLet me look at what the enhancer context looks like in previous experiments to understand the API, and also check what documentation might exist in sources/.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":14076,"cache_read_input_tokens":63056,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":14076,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":8},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"aa443835-14f9-43a2-a882-6515be006913","uuid":"73da6159-59e3-432c-bd05-397ca1b3c1e4","request_id":"req_vrtx_011CcCUmtWizeZN96zef4uNL"}
