{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_vrtx_01QnMni9kgoSv18x9gqv9UGv","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# Experiment 1: Happy Path\n2\t\n3\t**Result: PASS**\n4\t\n5\t## What was tested\n6\t\n7\tBuild-time Hibernate entity enhancement using the Hibernate ORM 6.6.51.Final-redhat-00001\n8\tEnhancer API, deployed to EAP 8.2.0.Alpha-CR39 with `jboss.as.jpa.classtransformer=false`.\n9\t\n10\t## Verification results\n11\t\n12\t| Check | Result |\n13\t|-------|--------|\n14\t| Entity enhanced at build time | PASS -- 1077 -> 5930 bytes |\n15\t| Implements ManagedEntity | PASS |\n16\t| Implements PersistentAttributeInterceptable (lazy loading) | PASS |\n17\t| Implements SelfDirtinessTracker | PASS |\n18\t| @EnhancementInfo annotation present | PASS -- version=6.6.51.Final-redhat-00001 |\n19\t| Deploy to EAP with classtransformer=false | PASS |\n20\t| Entity create/read via servlet | PASS |\n21\t| HHH90009001 trace message | Not emitted (expected for ORM 6.6.x) |\n22\t\n23\t## Key observations\n24\t\n25\t- Enhancement adds `$$_hibernate_*` fields and methods to the entity class\n26\t  (entityEntryHolder, attributeInterceptor, tracker, etc.)\n27\t- The `@EnhancementInfo` annotation records the Hibernate ORM version used\n28\t  for enhancement, enabling version mismatch detection at deploy time\n29\t- With `classtransformer=false`, the runtime enhancer is disabled and the\n30\t  server uses the pre-enhanced bytecode directly\n31\t- The server log shows `jboss.as.jpa.classtransformer: false` was respected\n32\t- HHH90009001 (\"Skipping enhancement -- already annotated with @EnhancementInfo\")\n33\t  is not emitted in ORM 6.6.x as noted in the experiment description\n34\t\n35\t## Environment\n36\t\n37\t- EAP: 8.2.0.Alpha-CR39\n38\t- Hibernate ORM: 6.6.51.Final-redhat-00001\n39\t- Java: OpenJDK 21.0.4 (Temurin)\n40\t- Enhancement method: Direct Enhancer API (EnhancerImpl + ByteBuddyState)\n41\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"aa443835-14f9-43a2-a882-6515be006913","uuid":"d5b354ea-4190-4e63-99a4-15ef9fae1785","timestamp":"2026-06-19T10:42:55.630Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/home/vsalbaba/Workspace/experiment/teach-me-ralph-loops/presentation-test-run-last/results/01-PASS-happy-path.md","content":"# Experiment 1: Happy Path\n\n**Result: PASS**\n\n## What was tested\n\nBuild-time Hibernate entity enhancement using the Hibernate ORM 6.6.51.Final-redhat-00001\nEnhancer API, deployed to EAP 8.2.0.Alpha-CR39 with `jboss.as.jpa.classtransformer=false`.\n\n## Verification results\n\n| Check | Result |\n|-------|--------|\n| Entity enhanced at build time | PASS -- 1077 -> 5930 bytes |\n| Implements ManagedEntity | PASS |\n| Implements PersistentAttributeInterceptable (lazy loading) | PASS |\n| Implements SelfDirtinessTracker | PASS |\n| @EnhancementInfo annotation present | PASS -- version=6.6.51.Final-redhat-00001 |\n| Deploy to EAP with classtransformer=false | PASS |\n| Entity create/read via servlet | PASS |\n| HHH90009001 trace message | Not emitted (expected for ORM 6.6.x) |\n\n## Key observations\n\n- Enhancement adds `$$_hibernate_*` fields and methods to the entity class\n  (entityEntryHolder, attributeInterceptor, tracker, etc.)\n- The `@EnhancementInfo` annotation records the Hibernate ORM version used\n  for enhancement, enabling version mismatch detection at deploy time\n- With `classtransformer=false`, the runtime enhancer is disabled and the\n  server uses the pre-enhanced bytecode directly\n- The server log shows `jboss.as.jpa.classtransformer: false` was respected\n- HHH90009001 (\"Skipping enhancement -- already annotated with @EnhancementInfo\")\n  is not emitted in ORM 6.6.x as noted in the experiment description\n\n## Environment\n\n- EAP: 8.2.0.Alpha-CR39\n- Hibernate ORM: 6.6.51.Final-redhat-00001\n- Java: OpenJDK 21.0.4 (Temurin)\n- Enhancement method: Direct Enhancer API (EnhancerImpl + ByteBuddyState)\n","numLines":41,"startLine":1,"totalLines":41}}}
